{"tid":1265132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好忘記今次係香港人史上最團結嘅一次","createTime":"2019-06-29T04:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T03:48:06.000Z","uid":247463,"like":61,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f54a2efbd2396d2201c900f1c2a24fc72ba8a9","tid":1265132,"uid":247463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T04:53:05.000Z","msg":"依兩日見大家開始攰<br />\n又話好似風向轉緊<br />\n吹到好似就嚟失敗咁<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">醒吓啦</span><br />\n香港人係前所未有咁形勢大好呀<br />\n以往每年最多咪10萬人行吓七一<br />\n喂今次團結咗200萬人喎<br />\n係2003年反23條嘅4倍呀<br />\n連空姐、南亞、左膠都大和解<br />\n一個月前有無人會想像到<br />\n重要每日極速進化<br />\n咁點會處於下風呀<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 巴絲們一定要十卜babykingdom同香討嘅jm同ching<br />\n靠晒佢地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bd201fc91b15bfc243b197fd532dec2bf1e713","tid":1265132,"uid":82640,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T04:54:08.000Z","msg":"心諗轉乜撚風<br />\n政治疲憊唧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad126d5d43d7e4930618b9ad3f39f9b124e95895","tid":1265132,"uid":247463,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c3bd201fc91b15bfc243b197fd532dec2bf1e713","tid":1265132,"uid":82640,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T04:54:08.000Z","msg":"心諗轉乜撚風<br />\n政治疲憊唧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T04:58:00.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n所以要不斷扶持身邊嘅人"},{"pid":"a32cc5bb85997d568e7db49aef58c31fed88b000","tid":1265132,"uid":247463,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T10:14:28.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"ef116e312911f01916e3b9e4e0833189fe6476dc","tid":1265132,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T10:15:12.000Z","ms